 * Spider — unit tests.
 *
 * Tests rig lifecycle, walk priority ordering, engine execution (clockwork
 * and quick), failure propagation, and CDC-driven writ transitions.
 *
 * Uses in-memory Stacks backend and mock Guild singleton.
